r networks. But it=E2=80=99s disingenuous for management to suggest to MSNB=
C employees that their network is in a stronger position after its own unco=
upling from a $163 billion conglomerate.

The far more likely outcome, as I=E2=80=99ve noted before, is that SpinCo w=
ill be positioned for a sale to private equity when the tax burden lifts, t=
wo years after the spin goes into effect. And then the grinfuckers will rea=
lly have at it, meticulously monetizing the decline curve. The notion that =
SpinCo can somehow avoid this fate
because of all its positive cash flow skirts the fact that the cable busine=
ss is in terminal decline, and there is no strategy in place to position th=
e assets for a lucrative future in digital or streaming=E2=80=94at least no=
t without making those assets much, much smaller.

But of course, even Laz=E2=80=99s career transition contains its own elemen=
t of spin. His appointment atop SpinCo has been framed as a vote of confide=
nce in the company=E2=80=99s future: Comcast wouldn=E2=80=99t put a talente=
d executive in charge of SpinCo if it wasn=E2=80=99t serious about making i=
t a success, the line goes. And, to be sure, Laz, a very talented executive=
, has an opportunity here to position himself for even bigger roles in the =
future if he manages the spinoff well and executes the eventual sale. (He=
=E2=80=99ll also almost certainly make a mint for himself.)

But it=E2=80=99s also important to remember that Laz ended up overseeing th=
ese assets because he lost the real battle for power at
NBCUniversal to Donna Langley, as my partner Matt Belloni recently noted ( =
https://puck.news/what-donna-langleys-promotion-means-for-nbcuniversal/?utm=
_campaign=3DIn+the+Room+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F4%2F24%29&utm_content=3DIn+Th=
e+Room+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F15%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_sourc=
e=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ). Langley is even more well-=
revered by her superiors and charges, alike. So it=E2=80=99s less a =E2=80=
=9Cvote of confidence=E2=80=9D in SpinCo than a consolation prize for a com=
pany veteran.

