ed top talent, =E2=80=9Cmost recently re-signing marquee host <b>Rachel Mad=
dow</b> to a new deal earlier this fall.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>I love Oliver=E2=
=80=94<i>seriously</i>, he=E2=80=99s a friend=E2=80=94but her departure is =
less of a unilateral decision than a conscious uncoupling. Alas, her
